reen</a> Setting <span class=\'tooltipsall classtoolTips9\' style=\'border-bottom:2px dotted #888;\'>Panel</span> in tooltips menu, just a few clicks, you can build a pretty Bullet Screen effect quickly, it looks like this:</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1653\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1413 size-full\" src=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bulletscreenpanel.png\" alt=\"Bullet Screen Setting\" width=\"987\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bulletscreenpanel.png 987w, https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bulletscreenpanel-300x109.png 300w, https://tomas.zhu.bz/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bulletscreenpanel-768x279.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 987px) 100vw, 987px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">wordpress bullets style custom panel</p>\n</div>\n<p>* Support custom Bullets Font Size<br />\n* Support custom Bullets Speed<br />\n* Support custom Bullets Font Color<br />\n* Support custom Bullets Amimate Opacity<br />\n* Support custom Bullets Class Name<br />\n* Support custom Bullets shows when:<br />\n# Mouse Over<br />\n# Mouse Leave<br />\n# Mouse Enter<br />\n# Mouse Out<br />\n# Mouse Move<br />\n# Mouse Up<br />\n# Mouse Down<br />\n# Double Click<br />\n# Click<br />\nJust a few clicks, You can use this <a href=\"https://tooltips.org/bullet-screen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">wordpress bullet plugin</a> to build bullets on your site quickly.</p>\n<p>* Optimized Bullet performance<br />\n* Fixed a Bullet Screen conflicts<br />\n* Support Bullet Screen effects for tooltips in the shortcode [tooltipslist] too<br />\n* Support Bullet Screen effects for tooltips in woocommerce products page too<br />\n* Support disable specific tooltips synonyms too<br />\n* Support disable specific tooltips synonyms in tooltips woocommerce addon<br />\n* Improve addons security</p>\n<p>I am developing a new version, if you have any feature request, it is very welcome 